HEADWORD: Upgrowth
<hw>Up"growth`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The process or
result of growing up; progress; development.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The new and mighty <qex>upgrowth</qex> of poetry in Italy.</q>
<rj><qau>J. R. Green.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
